<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ALAS, THERE'S NO HIGH-TECH PEACE &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (1,225 words) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Moved as BC-MESSY-WAR-MESSY-PEACE-ECONOMIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; DOES YOUR COMPANY REALLY NEED ANNUAL PAY RAISES? &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (725 words) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Moved as BC-BYEBYE-PAY-RAISES?-ECONOMIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; KASHMIR NEEDS LESS PAKISTANI BRINKSMANSHIP, MORE INDIAN
STATESMANSHIP &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
