<P>
   Last season's berry thing is gone and the glitter thing is gone.
Instead, there's lots of shimmer, such as the Stila All Over
Shimmer. Nars Galaxy Girl lipstick and Stila Kitten eye shadow are
shot with gold and give a very warm look for summer. A line that I
know will do very well is T. LeClerc. It's very sophisticated and
