</P>
<ANNOTATION>
   (STORY CAN END HERE _ OPTIONAL MATERIAL FOLLOWS)
</ANNOTATION>
<P>
   ``We estimate that we save our clients over $1 billion a year in
prescription drug costs,'' said Kevin Colgan, a spokesman for
