opposes the nomination of James Hormel as the U.S. ambassador to
Luxembourg on moral grounds, is being accused of hypocrisy.
Hormel's supporters say several of the senator's staff members
downloaded pornography from the Internet onto the Senate computer
system. By JUDY HOLLAND.
