on with the business of democracy and choose the man who will
replace him as the country's leader, Thabo Mbeki. By Suzanne Daley.
</P>
<P>
   CLEAN-AIR (Washington) _ Stymied by two court rulings setting
aside clean air standards, the EPA says it has a new way to force
power plants in 12 states to cut pollutants that contribute to smog
in the Northeast. By Matthew L. Wald.
</P>
<P>
   FILM-RATINGS-ENFORCE (Undated) _ What kids around the country
