<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-14 20:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5164 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LEWIS-TRIAL-BOS &LR;      06-14 0744
