<HEADER>
A5320 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-CONGRESS-KO     06-14 0048
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-CONGRESS-KOSOVO-HNS </SLUG>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 
Monday, June 14, 1999
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
Editors: &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
CONGRESS-KOSOVO (Washington) _ The Congress-Kosovo story will not
move tonight on the Hearst News wire service. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Houston Chronicle  &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
