<HEADLINE>
ASTROS MANAGER TO UNDERGO BRAIN SURGERY TUESDAY 

</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  (note: also moved on sports wire as BBN-ASTROS-DIERKER) 
 
By DAVID BARRON 
c.1999 Houston Chronicle 
 
<TEXT>
